[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

You open 1\S and partner responds 2\H.  

Partner has shown 11+ points and at least 4 \Hs. Your hand revalues to 16 points in support of \Hs, where you know you have an 8-card fit or better. You bid 4\H confidently.}

